      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using validation metric of mean absolute percentage error (MAPE). MAPE of 8.3% across five operating points; maximum single-point deviation of 12.7% at 4 L/min, 3500 RPM. All predictions within combined experimental and model uncertainty bounds. Exceeds MRL 2 output comparison requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
