      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) is the standard regulatory metric for blood pump hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Relative hemolysis index RH = NIH_device / NIH_predicate is the acceptance criterion. Both QoIs are directly relevant to the COU decision and have established clinical significance."
    },
