      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (same CAD files as simulation). Operating conditions span the CPB clinical range (2–6 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM). Bovine blood is accepted surrogate for human blood in hemolysis studies. Validation activities are highly relevant to the COU."
